title: Past Lives - Discography
description:
Discography of a not-so popular band known as Past Lives, made up of members of The Blood Brothers, the band got their start in late 2007 after The Blood Brothers disbanded. Vocalist Jordan Blilie, bassist Morgan Henderson, and drummer Mark Gajadhar joined with former Blood Brothers guitarist Devin Welch. 

Official Releases:
Strange Symmetry EP (2008)
The Journal of Popular Noise - Volume 1, Issue 7 (2008)
Tapestry of Webs (2008)

Bonus:
Daytrotter Session (2013)
KEXP Session 
Live at The Showbox

SEED OR ELSE
